  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/e40aa1480be078d409486719cfa0a628.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/e40aa1480be078d409486719cfa0a628.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Reknum: Fantasy of Dreams</i> is a 2.5D adventure and exploration game that combines action and the magic of dreams. Join Cheri on her epic quest to uncover the secrets of a dream world filled with strange creatures, puzzles, and surreal landscapes. With hand-drawn frame-by-frame graphics and an instrumental soundtrack that captures the essence of a dream, every step of this journey is a work of art.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 <strong>2.5D Adventure:</strong> Explore a dreamlike world full of secrets in an action-packed 2.5D environment reminiscent of classic Metroidvania games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/af3f6034decfc3b9cda0d65f5d84a6c7.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/af3f6034decfc3b9cda0d65f5d84a6c7.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span>🌙 <strong>Hand-Drawn Art:</strong> Enjoy beautiful hand-drawn graphics frame by frame, giving the game a unique and charming style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/1990fd3b4db2c3065e88c87f60f9eada.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/1990fd3b4db2c3065e88c87f60f9eada.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=450 /></span>🌙 <strong>Instrumental Soundtrack:</strong> Immerse yourself in an instrumental soundtrack that perfectly complements the magical and mysterious atmosphere of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/c0592ca6b8a05750384173e407036790.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/c0592ca6b8a05750384173e407036790.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span>🌙 <strong>Explore and Solve:</strong> Traverse fantastic landscapes, face mysterious creatures, and solve puzzles to uncover the secrets of the dream world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/94c45ee97fb1488c0289352331b34562.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/94c45ee97fb1488c0289352331b34562.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span>🌙 <strong>Challenging Gameplay:</strong> Gain new abilities and powers as you progress, facing enemies and obstacles that will test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/d2d7ea662ddadae19cfdabc93f4fb270.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/d2d7ea662ddadae19cfdabc93f4fb270.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an unforgettable adventure full of mystery, magic, and challenges. Are you ready to uncover the secrets of dreams and save the world trapped between them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/e40aa1480be078d409486719cfa0a628.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/e40aa1480be078d409486719cfa0a628.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Reknum: Fantasy of Dreams</i> is a 2.5D adventure and exploration game that combines action and the magic of dreams. Join Cheri on her epic quest to uncover the secrets of a dream world filled with strange creatures, puzzles, and surreal landscapes. With hand-drawn frame-by-frame graphics and an instrumental soundtrack that captures the essence of a dream, every step of this journey is a work of art.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 <strong>2.5D Adventure:</strong> Explore a dreamlike world full of secrets in an action-packed 2.5D environment reminiscent of classic Metroidvania games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/af3f6034decfc3b9cda0d65f5d84a6c7.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/af3f6034decfc3b9cda0d65f5d84a6c7.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span>🌙 <strong>Hand-Drawn Art:</strong> Enjoy beautiful hand-drawn graphics frame by frame, giving the game a unique and charming style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/1990fd3b4db2c3065e88c87f60f9eada.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/1990fd3b4db2c3065e88c87f60f9eada.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=450 /></span>🌙 <strong>Instrumental Soundtrack:</strong> Immerse yourself in an instrumental soundtrack that perfectly complements the magical and mysterious atmosphere of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/c0592ca6b8a05750384173e407036790.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/c0592ca6b8a05750384173e407036790.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span>🌙 <strong>Explore and Solve:</strong> Traverse fantastic landscapes, face mysterious creatures, and solve puzzles to uncover the secrets of the dream world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/94c45ee97fb1488c0289352331b34562.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/94c45ee97fb1488c0289352331b34562.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span>🌙 <strong>Challenging Gameplay:</strong> Gain new abilities and powers as you progress, facing enemies and obstacles that will test your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras/d2d7ea662ddadae19cfdabc93f4fb270.avif?t=1734773850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582760/extras_big/d2d7ea662ddadae19cfdabc93f4fb270.avif?t=1734773850 width=800 height=452 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an unforgettable adventure full of mystery, magic, and challenges. Are you ready to uncover the secrets of dreams and save the world trapped between them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
